skin-52971a3886a2_0_st.name: StatTrak™ Glock-18 | Moonrise (Factory New)
skin-52971a3886a2_0_st.description:
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

This item tracks Confirmed Kills.

The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. A randomized city landscape in the foreground gives way to a full moon and purple night sky.\n\nLook for the North Star
